      "author_name": "MADHU KUMAR",
      "rating": 1,
      "review_text": "\"I want to warn everyone about one of the costliest hospitals in Bangalore. My family and I had a terrible experience there.\n\nWhile our patient was admitted, the hospital team tormented us day after day for payments. The room rents were excessively high and provided no value for the amount we paid. Most distressingly, when the patient was in a critical, near-death condition, the entire team acted unprofessionally. They seemed to be prolonging the situation just to extract more money from us, the patient's family.\n\nTragically, we recently lost my beloved brother in this very hospital.\n\nI am requesting you all to please be very careful. Do your research and think twice before choosing this hospital.\"",
      "review_time": "2025-12-13T05:02:25Z"
    },
